        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Drilling in Our Backyards Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Department of the Interior from issuing a permit for any oil and gas drilling operation that is located within 1,500 feet from a home, business, school, or other building that requires special protection.</p>]]></text>
